backdoor_protection.desc: Structure takes reduced damage, and quickly regenerates any damage taken while no enemy creeps are nearby.

backdoor_protection_in_base.desc: Structure takes reduced damage, and quickly regenerates any damage taken while no enemy creeps are nearby.

filler_ability.desc: Activate to restore health and mana regeneration over time and gain 50XP for each time the shrine was activated

necronomicon_warrior_last_will.desc: Deals damage to the unit that kills the Necronomicon Warrior.

necronomicon_warrior_mana_burn.desc: Mana burned per hit, a portion of which is dealt as damage.

necronomicon_archer_mana_burn.desc: Launches an arrow that burns away the targeted unit's mana, dealing damage equal to the amount of mana burned.

necronomicon_archer_purge.desc:
Dispels positive buffs from enemies and slows their movement speed.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

courier_go_to_secretshop.desc: Sends the courier to your team's secret shop

courier_shield.desc: Summons a protective shield around the courier

courier_burst.desc: The courier gains a burst of speed for 6 seconds

kobold_taskmaster_speed_aura.desc: The Kobold Foreman's cruel efficiency increases his movement speed and the movement speed of all nearby allies.

ogre_bruiser_ogre_smash.desc: Ogre slowly charges a big attack stunning for 2.4 seconds and dealing 200 + 8% of their current HP as damage to all units in front of him.

giant_wolf_intimidate.desc: The Giant Wolf's ferocious roar reduces all nearby enemies total attack damage.

hill_troll_rally.desc: Skeleton's allies gain bonus attack damage. This Aura stacks.

berserker_troll_break.desc: Whenever Hill Troll Berserker attacks a unit it applies break to it.

spawnlord_master_stomp.desc: Stomps the ground, dealing damage to nearby units and reducing their base physical armor by 50%.

spawnlord_master_freeze.desc: Causes the next attack to petrify the enemy, rooting them and dealing 75 damage per second.

gnoll_assassin_envenomed_weapon.desc: The Vhoul Assassin has soaked his weapons in his own blend of painful predator venoms that causes his enemies' natural regeneration to work against themselves. Heroes recover from the poison more quickly.

ghost_frost_attack.desc: The Ghost launches an eerie attack that chills her enemies to their bones.

neutral_spell_immunity.desc: This creature does not feel the effects of most magical spells.

mud_golem_rock_destroy.desc: On death, Mud Golems shatter into several Shard Golems.

warpine_raider_seed_shot.desc: Hucks a seed at a target, slowing and damaging it. The seed can bounce multiple times to nearby targets.

mud_golem_hurl_boulder.desc: Hurls a boulder at the target, damaging and stunning them.
mud_golem_hurl_boulder.lore: \"Why do they hesitate? What are they afraid of throwing?\"

giant_wolf_critical_strike.desc: The Giant Wolf's ferocious attacks occasionally tear a vital tendon, inflicting critical damage.

alpha_wolf_critical_strike.desc: The cruel Alpha Wolf attacks his enemy's unprotected vitals at every opportunity, inflicting critical damage.

alpha_wolf_command_aura.desc: The Alpha Wolf's ruthless attacks do extra damage. His commanding presence inspires nearby allies to attack ruthlessly as well.

frostbitten_golem_time_warp_aura.desc: Coming from a different era, the Frostbitten Golem has an innate control of time, speeding up the cooldowns of all nearby allies.

ice_shaman_incendiary_bomb.desc: The Ice Shaman chucks a blue flame towards an enemy unit or building, dealing damage over time.

ancient_rock_golem_weakening_aura.desc: The Rock Golem's imposing figure makes enemies more susceptible to Physical Damage.

black_drake_magic_amplification_aura.desc: The Black Drakes' gaze make enemies more susceptible to Spell Damage.

tornado_tempest.desc: The Tornado's overpowering winds slow all nearby enemies, flinging debris at them and inflicting damage every second. Enemies closer to the center of the Tornado take more damage.

creep_siege.desc: Reinforced Units and Buildings Deal Bonus Damage to other Reinforced Units and Buildings and take less attack damage from other units.

creep_piercing.desc: Piercing Units Deal Bonus Damage to non-hero, non-heavy units and reduced damage to heroes and heavy units.

creep_irresolute.desc: Runty Units Deal reduced damage to hero units.

enraged_wildkin_tornado.desc: CHANNELED - The Wildwing calls on the spirit of the wind, creating a sentient Tornado that he can control. The Tornado slows nearby enemies and does damage. It is invulnerable and can move anywhere.

enraged_wildkin_hurricane.desc: The Wildwing Ripper calls on the spirit of the wind, creating a hurricane that can push a unit in the direction of Wildwing Ripper's choice.

kobold_disarm.desc: Every third attack Kobold Soldier will disarm its target temporarily. Attack counter doesn't increase while ability is on cooldown.

enraged_wildkin_toughness_aura.desc: The Wildwing Ripper's fury numbs it to attacks and inspires nearby allies to withstand more blows.

flagbearer_creep_aura_effect.desc: The Flagbearer inspires all allies, granting them bonus health regeneration.

granite_golem_hp_aura.desc: Increases the health capacity of nearby units.

satyr_trickster_purge.desc:
The Satyr Banisher knows every trick in the book, allowing him to dispel debuffs from allies or buffs from enemies. His trickery also slows the enemy's movement.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

satyr_soulstealer_mana_burn.desc: The Satyr Mindstealer removes a fragment of his enemy's soul, burning away mana equal to 20 + 2x the target's intelligence, and dealing damage equal to the amount of mana burned.

satyr_hellcaller_shockwave.desc: The Satyr Tormenter tears open an unstable rift to the underworld, creating a shockwave that travels in a line along the ground, dealing damage to enemies it hits.

satyr_hellcaller_unholy_aura.desc: The Satyr Tormenter's demonic communion allows him to emanate regenerative power, increasing the health regeneration of himself and all nearby allies.

forest_troll_high_priest_heal.desc: The Hill Troll Priest lays his holy blessing upon the target ally, replenishing some health.

harpy_scout_take_off.desc: Harpy Scout gains flying movement at the cost of movement speed. Consumes mana while active.

furbolg_enrage_attack_speed.desc: When Hellbear dies, all nearby allies go into a frenzy gaining attack speed for a short amount of time.

furbolg_enrage_damage.desc: When Hellbear Smasher dies, all nearby allies go into a rampage gaining bonus attack damage for a short amount of time.

kobold_tunneler_prospecting.desc: Kobolds are adept at finding gold, increasing nearby allied heroes' GPM.

harpy_storm_chain_lightning.desc: The Harpy Stormcrafter releases a high-voltage bolt of electricity at the target enemy, dealing damage. The bolt jumps to other nearby enemies, losing power with each jump.

big_thunder_lizard_wardrums_aura.desc: The rhythm of the Thunderhide's heartbeat increases the attack speed and accuracy of nearby allies.

black_dragon_dragonhide_aura.desc: The Ancient Black Dragon's dreaded presence grants nearby allies additional armor. This bonus can stack with itself.

black_dragon_fireball.desc: Hurls a fire blast on the ground, igniting the area in a 300 radius for 8 seconds. Enemies caught in the fire will take 85 damage per second.

mudgolem_cloak_aura.desc: This creature protects its allies with a Magic resistance aura. Creeps are better protected.

black_dragon_splash_attack.desc: The Black Dragon's explosive attacks are felt by all nearby enemies.

blue_dragonspawn_sorcerer_evasion.desc: The Drakken Sentinel has assumed a partially ethereal form, making him difficult to hit with attacks.

blue_dragonspawn_overseer_evasion.desc: The Drakken Armorer moves about quickly, making him difficult to hit with attacks.

spawnlord_aura.desc: Gives lifesteal and health regeneration to nearby allies.

blue_dragonspawn_overseer_devotion_aura.desc: The Drakken Armorer is wholly devoted to his cause, increasing his tolerance for physical attacks. Nearby allies are similarly devoted to the Overseer and are able to withstand more blows.

big_thunder_lizard_slam.desc: The Ancient Thunderhide slams his mammoth body against the ground. The shock damages nearby enemies and throws them off their footing. Heroes regain their balance more quickly.

big_thunder_lizard_frenzy.desc: The Ancient Thunderhide works an ally into a frenzy, causing his ally to have increased attack speed.

forest_troll_high_priest_mana_aura.desc: Provides bonus mana regeneration to all nearby allies.

forest_troll_high_priest_heal_amp_aura.desc: Provides bonus Heal Amplification to all nearby allies.

roshan_halloween_wave_of_force.desc: After a delay, Roshan smashes the ground, causing massive radial damage in an area around him, knocking back all enemies. The closer to Roshan the enemy is, the more damage it takes.

roshan_halloween_toss.desc: Roshan tosses a nearby enemy unit at an enemy that is further away.

roshan_halloween_shell.desc: Roshan becomes immune to physical damage, but takes enhanced magical damage for a brief time. When Roshan uses Shell, all ability and item cooldowns are refreshed.

roshan_halloween_apocalypse.desc: Roshan launches devastating beams of incineration from the sky at all enemy heroes outside of 400 range, but within 1200 range.

roshan_halloween_burn.desc: Roshan breathes a lethal arc of searing fire.

roshan_halloween_summon.desc: Roshan calls a group of Roshlings to aid him.

roshan_halloween_fireball.desc: Roshan launches a number of slow moving fireballs at all nearby enemies.

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl10_l.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl15_l.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl20_l.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl25_l.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl10_r.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl15_r.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl20_r.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

ad_special_bonus_gold_lvl25_r.desc: Associated ability not drafted, have some gold!

seasonal_throw_snowball.desc: Throw a snowball at an ally or enemy.
seasonal_throw_snowball.lore: Hand crafted at the perfect temperature.

seasonal_summon_snowman.lore: He'll stay friends as long as he can.

seasonal_summon_penguin.desc: Summon a friendly penguin who slides around. Each time a hero bumps the penguin, it gains speed and lasts a bit longer.
seasonal_summon_penguin.lore: Nothing gets age-old enemies to set aside their differences quite like a penguin to play with.

seasonal_decorate_tree.desc: Give any tree a delightfully seasonal touch.
seasonal_decorate_tree.lore: Festive trappings for even the bloodiest of battlefields.

seasonal_festive_firework.desc: Shoot a firework into the air.
seasonal_festive_firework.lore: There's nothing more festive than explosions!

frostivus2018_throw_snowball.desc:
Throw a snowball at an enemy, damaging and stunning all enemy units around it.

Note: All Frosthaven consumables have a shared cooldown.
frostivus2018_throw_snowball.lore: Enjoy a bold, rocky center with a packed-ice crust!

frostivus2018_summon_snowman.desc:
Summons a snowman that taunts nearby enemies.

Note: All Frosthaven consumables have a shared cooldown.

frostivus2018_decorate_tree.desc:
Decorate a tree with blinking lights that damage nearby enemies.

Note: All Frosthaven consumables have a shared cooldown.
frostivus2018_decorate_tree.lore: Who knew a few twinkling lights could be so deadly?

frostivus2018_festive_firework.desc:
Fires a global range firework that explodes over a given area, damaging enemies, blinding them, and providing vision for 10 seconds.

Note: All Frosthaven consumables have a shared cooldown.
frostivus2018_festive_firework.lore: There's nothing more festive than explosions!

high_five.desc: Throw your hand (or handy appendage) in the air!

seasonal_summon_ti9_balloon.desc: No one can resist the sky snake's goofy charms.

seasonal_ti9_banner.desc: Plant your personal battle standard to mark this battleground as yours!

seasonal_ti9_shovel.desc: Dig around the map for buried treasure!

seasonal_ti9_monkey.desc: He'll fling filth at your enemies so you don't have to.

seasonal_10th_anniversary_party_hat.desc: Put on your fancy party hat to celebrate the 10th Anniversary of Dota 2! The hat will stay on your head until you die a horrible death.

plus_high_five.desc: Throw your hand (or handy appendage) in the air!

plus_guild_banner.desc: Plant your guild's banner to mark this battleground for you all!
